message.body: Might you be in the neighborhood, my dear?
Yeah, just fixin to do my laundry. Are you??
I was! Now I'm in Berwyn, but I'll be back later! Do you have dinner plans?
Going to check out a new beer garden-type place called Morgan's Pier on delaware ave around 7:30-8
Drat :-( Maybe coffee or something tomorrow afternoon?
Yeah, let me know when you're around
I'm just finishing a late breakfast at the diner- would you be up for coffee or something at 1?
Yay! I'll meet you at your place then.
